				.carousel-item.active
					img.d-block.w-100(src='assets/images/carousel-main/01.jpg', alt='First slide')
					.carousel-caption.d-flex.align-items-center
						.row
							.col-9.col-lg-8.mx-auto
								p.lead
									| VPL uses Schüco-brand top-quality thermally isolated aluminium profile systems for its windows and doors. The high-quality window and door elements impress with their elegant details in a slimline, beautiful look.
								p.phone.my-5
									| +88 159 85 9253
								button.btn.btn-lg.btn-outline-dark.px-5.py-4(type='button')
									| Обратный звонок
				.carousel-item
					img.d-block.w-100(src='assets/images/carousel-main/02.jpg', alt='Second slide')
					.carousel-caption.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center
						.jumbotron.w-75(style='background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .75)')
							h2.display-4
								| Some other lead
							p.lead
								| List key advantages of your product here
			a.carousel-control-prev(href='#carouselMain', role='button', data-slide='prev')
